```css
/* Component container */
.container {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 1rem;
}

/* Responsive classes */
.flex {
  display: flex;
}

.grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
  gap: 1rem;
}

/* Utility classes */
.text-center {
  text-align: center;
}

.mt-1 {
  margin-top: 1rem;
}

.mb-1 {
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.py-2 {
  padding-top: 2rem;
  padding-bottom: 2rem;
}
``` 